the easiest thing to do is this:

[code:u2g2ox3d]&lt;object name=&quot;player&quot;&gt;
  &lt;attr name=&quot;equipped_weapon_object&quot; type=&quot;object&quot;&gt;unarmed&lt;/attr&gt; // you'll need an 'equip' script to set that weapon to this attribute
